title: Luna Maya
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Mexican, Latin American, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Mexican food restaurant and bar. Marks the vegetarian and vegan items. Vegans could get burrito with spicy or cilantro lime potatoes; quesadilla with bean spread, caramelized onions, roasted poblano, enchiladas; a wrap and slaw, among others.
